definition: of or relating to the fourth power, a polynomial of the fourth degree
details:
adjective
- of or relating to the fourth power
noun
- a polynomial of the fourth degree
= synonyms: biquadratic polynomial, quartic polynomial
- an equation of the fourth degree
= synonyms: biquadratic equation
- an algebraic equation of the fourth degree
= synonyms: biquadrate, quartic, fourth power
